    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1001,"isDeleted":false,"id":"mod-1-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":376,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":268,"height":130,"seed":1001,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":15,"fontFamily":3,"text":"1. PulseClient\nmobula/pulse-client.ts\n\nOpens the WS, sends subscribe,\npings every 30s.\nReconnect 1s → 30s backoff.\nRe-subscribes on every reconnect.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"1. PulseClient\nmobula/pulse-client.ts\n\nOpens the WS, sends subscribe,\npings every 30s.\nReconnect 1s → 30s backoff.\nRe-subscribes on every reconnect.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

