    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1301,"isDeleted":false,"id":"mod-4-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":1016,"y":376,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":228,"height":130,"seed":1301,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":15,"fontFamily":3,"text":"4. Formatter + Bot\ncore/formatter.ts\ntelegram/bot.ts\n\nMarkdownV2 message.\nChart → DexScreener.\nBuy → pump.fun / Jupiter\n     / Uniswap (per chain).","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"4. Formatter + Bot\ncore/formatter.ts\ntelegram/bot.ts\n\nMarkdownV2 message.\nChart → DexScreener.\nBuy → pump.fun / Jupiter\n     / Uniswap (per chain).","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1400,"isDeleted":false,"id":"section-2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":560,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":600,"height":32,"seed":1400,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":22,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Pulse Stream V2 — wire format","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Pulse Stream V2 — wire format","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1500,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-sub","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":600,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","backgroundColor":"#ffe8cc","width":420,"height":340,"seed":1500,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1501,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-sub-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":612,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":392,"height":320,"seed":1501,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Subscribe (client → server, after open)\n\n{\n  type: 'pulse-v2',\n  authorization: <API_KEY>,\n  payload: {\n    assetMode: true,\n    compressed: false,\n    views: [{\n      name: 'fresh-tokens',\n      chainId: ['solana:solana','evm:8453','evm:1'],\n      poolTypes: ['pumpfun','raydium-v4',\n                  'uniswap-v2','uniswap-v3'],\n      sortBy: 'created_at',\n      sortOrder: 'desc',\n      limit: 50,\n      filters: {\n        liquidity: { gte: 2000 },\n        bonded:    { equals: false }\n      }\n    }]\n  }\n}\n\nNote: chainId / poolTypes go INSIDE the view,\nnot in payload.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Subscribe (client → server, after open)","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1600,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-msgs","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":480,"y":600,"strokeColor":"#c92a2a","backgroundColor":"#ffe3e3","width":420,"height":340,"seed":1600,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1601,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-msgs-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":496,"y":612,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":392,"height":320,"seed":1601,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Server messages (server → client)\n\ninit\n  { type, payload: { 'fresh-tokens':\n                     { data: [row, ...] } } }\n  → seed dedup, do NOT alert\n\nsync (~every 30s)\n  same shape as init\n  → REPLACE state, not merge\n\nnew-token\n  { type, payload:\n     { viewName, token: row } }\n  → dedup, score, alert\n\nupdate-token / remove-token\n  ignored (no first-alert relevance)\n\nrow is FLAT: address, chainId, symbol,\nliquidity, bonded, devHoldings,\nsnipersHoldings, top10Holdings, ...","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Server messages","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1700,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-quirks","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":920,"y":600,"strokeColor":"#5f3dc4","backgroundColor":"#e5dbff","width":340,"height":340,"seed":1700,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1701,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-quirks-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":936,"y":612,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":312,"height":320,"seed":1701,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Things that bit us\n\n1. chainId / poolTypes must sit\n   INSIDE the view object,\n   not in payload.\n\n2. Top-level field is `payload`,\n   not `data`.\n\n3. Init/sync data lives at\n   payload['fresh-tokens'].data\n\n4. Token row is flat:\n   devHoldings (NOT devHoldingsPercentage)\n   top10Holdings, snipersHoldings.\n\n5. Init = current view state,\n   not new launches.\n   Use it to seed dedup, never\n   to alert.\n\n6. Subscriptions don't persist\n   on reconnect — re-subscribe.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Things that bit us","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1800,"isDeleted":false,"id":"section-3","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":980,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":600,"height":32,"seed":1800,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":22,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Video script — 7 beats","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Video script — 7 beats","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1900,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-script","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":1020,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","width":1220,"height":360,"seed":1900,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1901,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-script-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":1036,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":1192,"height":340,"seed":1901,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":15,"fontFamily":3,"text":"1. The problem\n   Sniping fresh tokens is a race. By the time DexScreener lists a token, the move is already over.\n   You need the data BEFORE the public indexers do.\n\n2. Why Pulse Stream V2\n   One WebSocket. Every chain Mobula supports. Every DEX (pump.fun, Moonshot, Raydium, Uniswap).\n   Server-side filters: liquidity, bonded, holdings concentration, sort, limit. The wire is already clean.\n\n3. Architecture\n   Show the four boxes: PulseClient · SeenStore · QualityGate · Formatter+Bot. ~600 lines, no infra.\n\n4. Live demo\n   npm run dev. Logs: connecting → connected → subscribed. Wait for first new-token line.\n   Switch to Telegram, alert appears. Click Chart → DexScreener. Click Trade on pump.fun → token page.\n\n5. The score (0-100)\n   Holders count, holdings concentration (dev / snipers / top10), pool growth ratio, bonding %,\n   pro traders count, trending score. Bucketed into ELITE / GOOD / FAIR / LOW.\n\n6. Resilience\n   Auto-reconnect with exponential backoff. Re-subscribe on every reconnect.\n   SQLite dedup so the periodic sync replay never double-alerts.\n   Init snapshot is silent — only live new-token events become Telegram messages.\n\n7. Closing\n   Built on Mobula Pulse — the same stream used by exchanges and trading desks.\n   Code is open-source under MIT. Repo: github.com/Flotapponnier/pulse-sniper","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"video script","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25}
  ],
  "appState": {
    "gridSize": null,
    "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"
  },
  "files": {}
}
